data.description: Now entertaining offers between $870k - $899k. So much potential on this one. Greeted by AMAZING VIEWS you'll instantly feel a sense of relaxation. Sitting on a large 2.6 acre lot, there are endless possibilities. Home consists of 3 bedrooms & an optional 4th. Cozy fireplace w/ wood burning stove in living room. Large deck off the back of the home to take in the views. New SOLAR to save $$. There's also a 780sqft 2bd mobile home on the property which can be restored & rented to offset mtg.There are numerous fruit trees to include dragonfruit, avocado & newly updated irrigation system for entire property to be more efficient.  Custom tree house built for the kids. Multiple storage sheds. Gated area by guest home for pets. Ask about the ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 2.25% & 2/1 Rate Buydown
